{"tid":809781,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"息魔來了 淡淡贏哂","createTime":"2018-09-07T12:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T16:43:38.000Z","uid":165683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ff39aba8f980068f46b543412dd923836a8b4c6","tid":809781,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:33:37.000Z","msg":"Long-awaited wage growth posted a recovery high in August while payroll gains beat expectations and the unemployment rate held near a generational low of 3.9 percent, according to a Bureau of Labor Statistics report Friday.<br />\n<br />\nAverage hourly earnings rose 2.9 percent for the month on an annualized basis, while nonfarm payrolls grew by 201,000. Economists surveyed by Reuters had been expecting earnings to rise 2.7 percent, payrolls to increase by 191,000 and the jobless level to decline one-tenth of a point to 3.8 percent.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/09/07/us-nonfarm-payrolls-aug-2018.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F09%2F07%2Fus-nonfarm-payrolls-aug-2018.html&d=EAXJ%2Fs%2BQrGjAWLZqT%2Ff6zP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=78a9dafe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/09/07/us-nonfarm-payrolls-aug-2018.html</a>"},{"pid":"c4eb422b532de6b46c5365998cf6019c2e5a99e5","tid":809781,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"It comes finally<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c88a6a067886ccfa832462d7ebe1eb928ca34d","tid":809781,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4eb422b532de6b46c5365998cf6019c2e5a99e5","tid":809781,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"It comes finally<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:41:26.000Z","msg":"港女2分鐘直插100點<br />\n人民幣一齊插"},{"pid":"9e837a5ce